# This directory stores generated issue reports in a hierarchical structure:
#
# issues/
# ├── security/
# │   ├── critical/
# │   │   └── {issue_id}.md
# │   ├── high/
# │   ├── medium/
# │   └── low/
# ├── performance/
# │   ├── critical/
# │   ├── high/
# │   ├── medium/
# │   └── low/
# ├── architecture/
# │   ├── critical/
# │   ├── high/
# │   ├── medium/
# │   └── low/
# └── index.json
#
# Each issue is saved as a markdown file with a unique hash-based ID
# An index.json file at the root tracks all issues for quick lookup
